Translation of station coordinates from LAT LON to X Y related to the hypocenter location that is taken as origin (0,0)

How to use this folder:

1. chmod +x compile.sh      make an executable script to compile
2. ./compile.sh             compile fortran code
3. chmod +x runstations.sh  make an executable script to run code
4. ./runstations.sh         run the binary using your input file

input files:
stations_*.in

output files:
stations_*-utm.dat   name of stations and xy coordinates
utm.dat              only xy coordinates

see inside runstations.sh to see how the input file is read during the run-time
